H0.text: What is the name of the small fifth claw called on the side of a dog's foot . Dewclaw

H1.text: What is the name of the small fifth claw called on the side of a dog's foot . Auxiclaw

H2.text: What is the name of the small fifth claw called on the side of a dog's foot . Paraclaw

H3.text: What is the name of the small fifth claw called on the side of a dog's foot . Duclaw

A4.text: They walk on four toes, front and back, and have vestigial dewclaws on their front legs and on their rear legs. When a dog has extra dewclaws in addition to the usual one in the rear, the dog is said to be 'double dewclawed.'
